This page on SteamDB showcases a curated list of games tagged as 'Sandbox'. The Sandbox tag is applied to games that offer players significant creative freedom, providing them with the tools and environments to build, explore, and experiment. These games often include elements of construction, simulation, and world-building, allowing players to shape their own gameplay experiences. Games tagged as Sandbox can span various genres, such as strategy, building, survival, and more. This automatically updated page serves as a hub for discovering and learning about the diverse range of games where players have the power to shape their own in-game worlds.
